data.description: Nestled in the sought-after Arthur Heights community, this charming 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom two story seamlessly blends classic character with modern updates, offering a picturesque retreat just minutes away from vibrant Arnolds Park, scenic bike trails, state parks, and the pristine waters of East Lake Okoboji. With lake access and a tranquil setting, this home provides an idyllic escape with a perfect balance of country living and convenience. Step inside, and the seamless integration of old-world charm and contemporary amenities becomes immediately apparent. The entire home has been adorned with fresh wall and trim paint, and carpet creating a bright and airy atmosphere that complements the timeless architecture.  The heart of this home is undoubtedly the updated kitchen, where the kitchen features a large center island, ample storage, and a spacious layout that makes entertaining a delight.  This updated two-story exudes warmth and character, with a new roof, AC, that enhances the overall aesthetic appeal. The updates extend to the exterior, where a new deck awaits, offering a seamless transition between indoor and outdoor living. Imagine enjoying your morning coffee or hosting summer barbecues in this private oasis surrounded by the lush greenery of the beautiful flower gardens of the backyard. The five bedrooms are generously sized and bathed in natural light, providing comfortable retreats for family members or guests. With its prime location, thoughtful updates, and access to East Lake Okoboji, this property is a rare find that harmonizes a life of tranquility and convenience.
